  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this surveillance is to collect Safety and Effectiveness information for
      Long term Use of Somatropin for Patients with a Small for Gestational Age (SGA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All the patients whom an investigator prescribes Genotropin should be registered
      consecutively until the number of subjects reaches target number in order to extract patients
      enrolled into the investigation at random.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
